The paper focuses on generating informative comments directly from source code using natural language processing techniques. This falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The use of natural language models and grammar rules also suggests a connection to computational linguistics (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the form of automated comment generation.
